 2019-06132019-05-31,  ,  ,  ECCC, 
ActFederal Sustainable Development Act
SubjectOrder Amending the Schedule to the Federal Sustainable Development Act
PrecisORDER AMENDING THE SCHEDULE TO THE FEDERAL SUSTAINABLE DEVELOPMENT ACT in order to make The National Capital Commission and the Jacques-Cartier and Champlain Bridges Inc. subject to the Act's application, and thereby require the two Crown Corporations to contribute to the development and reporting on the Federal Sustainable Development Strategy and to develop and report on their own individual sustainable development strategy.
